---

AGENT STRUCTURE
---------------

Each agent folder should contain:
```
agent-name/
├── agent.md       # Main agent configuration (required)
├── README.md      # Agent documentation
└── *.md           # Additional resources (optional)
```

---

AGENT VS SKILL
--------------

| Feature        | Skill                    | Agent                     |
|----------------|--------------------------|---------------------------|
| Purpose        | Knowledge/patterns       | Autonomous execution      |
| Task Nature    | Guidance/rules/patterns  | Multi-step workflow       |
| Mode           | Assists Claude           | Acts independently        |
| Best For       | Any task needing guidance | Autonomous complex tasks  |
| Example        | "Add database query"     | "Build entire service"    |
| Selection      | ALWAYS invoke on match   | ALWAYS invoke on match    |

